  "texts": [
    "AI contributes its knowledge to humans by providing recommendations with AI explanations serving as a means of representing its detailed reasoning [69].",
    "These explanations could facilitate the collaborative synthesis of human and AI intelligence, allowing them to combine insights into different features for final decisions.",
    "However, when conflicting views arise, current interfaces provide limited support for the communication and exchange of human and AI knowledge [79].",
    "To address this, we propose Human-AI Deliberation to resolve conflicts through natural discussions.The second challenge concerns human reliance on AI suggestions [8,85,87,89,137].",
    "Achieving complementary performance relies on human decision-makers' ability to judiciously determine when to consider AI recommendations and when to be skeptical [16,105,137]."
  ],
